Blocks.childText: BRIGHT GOLDEN CITY. Concluded. CHORUS. In that beau ti ful cit y, In that bright gold - en cit y, We shall meet one a - noth - er a gain; In that beau ti ful cit y, a-gain, In that bright gold - en cit y, With Je sus for ev er we'll reign.
